cmput301w16t08.scaling_pancake.models

Class Instrument

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmput301w16t08.scaling_pancake.models.Instrument

  • public class Instrument
extends java.lang.Object
    Instrument is meant represent an instrument owned by a specific User (called the owner), and contains a list of Bids on the instrument
    See Also:
    User, Bid
